sequenceDiagram
    participant EPP as llm-d-inference-scheduler<br/>(EPP)
    participant Sidecar as Routing Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP · HTTPS · TLS 1.2+
    participant Allowlist as SSRF Allowlist<br/>(In-Process)
    participant Prefiller as Remote Prefiller<br/>HTTP(S) · Configurable Port
    participant Decoder as Local vLLM Decoder<br/>8001/TCP · HTTP(S)

    Note over EPP,Decoder: Flow 1: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL V2)

    EPP->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Header: x-prefiller-host-port: <host:port><br/>Body: OpenAI-compatible request

    Sidecar->>Allowlist: Validate prefiller host<br/>(if SSRF protection enabled)

    alt Host not in allowlist
        Allowlist-->>Sidecar: REJECT
        Sidecar-->>EPP: HTTP 403 Forbidden
    else Host allowed (or SSRF disabled)
        Allowlist-->>Sidecar: ALLOW

        Note over Sidecar,Prefiller: Phase 1: Prefill
        Sidecar->>Prefiller: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>+ kv_transfer_params: {do_remote_decode: true}<br/>+ max_completion_tokens: 1
        Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Response with kv_transfer_params:<br/>{block_ids, engine_id, host, port, tokens}

        Note over Sidecar,Decoder: Phase 2: Decode with KV Cache
        Sidecar->>Decoder: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>+ kv_transfer_params from prefiller<br/>+ Original request body
        Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streaming/Full completion response
        Sidecar-->>EPP: Forward response to caller
    end

    Note over EPP,Decoder: Flow 2: Direct Decode (No Prefill Header)

    EPP->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(no x-prefiller-host-port header)
    Sidecar->>Decoder: Forward request directly<br/>HTTP(S)/8001
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Completion response
    Sidecar-->>EPP: Forward response to caller

    Note over EPP,Decoder: Flow 3: Passthrough (Non-Completion Endpoints)

    EPP->>Sidecar: ANY /* (catch-all)<br/>HTTPS/8000
    Sidecar->>Decoder: Forward as-is<br/>HTTP(S)/8001
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Response
    Sidecar-->>EPP: Forward response

    Note over Sidecar,Allowlist: Background: SSRF Allowlist Maintenance

    Sidecar->>Allowlist: Start InferencePool watcher<br/>(if --ssrf-allowlist enabled)
    loop Every 30s resync + event-driven
        Allowlist->>Allowlist: Watch InferencePool CR<br/>(inference.networking.x-k8s.io/v1alpha2)
        Allowlist->>Allowlist: Watch Pods matching<br/>InferencePool label selector
        Allowlist->>Allowlist: Rebuild allowed<br/>IPs/hostnames set
    end
